---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Last Time I"
  description="Privacy policy for the Last Time I iOS app."
>
  <main class="page-wrap">
    <a href="/lasttimei" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Last Time I</a>

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <p><strong>Last Time I</strong> does not collect, store, or share any personal data. All your data is stored locally on your device and never leaves it.</p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>All items and history are stored locally using on-device storage</li>
      <li>No data is transmitted to external servers</li>
      <li>No analytics or tracking is used</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Notifications</h2>
    <p>The app may request permission to send local notifications. These are used solely to remind you about tasks you have configured. Notification data never leaves your device.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This app does not use any third-party services, analytics, or advertising.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact: <a href="mailto:amanmittal.work@gmail.com">amanmittal.work@gmail.com</a></p>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  body {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d4f5dd 0%, #eefaf1 35%, #ffffff 100%) !important;
  }
</style>

<style>
  .page-wrap {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 24px 40px;
    font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: #1d1d1f; }

  h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .updated {
    color: #86868b;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 28px 0 10px;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  p {
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    padding-left: 18px;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  li {
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  a {
    color: #30D158;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  a:hover { color: #28b84c; }
</style>
